Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.26,0:27:57.83,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,, {\i1}¡No escondas tu juventud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.83,0:28:00.83,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Fushigi shitakute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.83,0:28:00.83,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Quiero hacer lo misterioso{\i0}
